data.description: Location! Location! Location!. Great Clovis neighborhood, down the street from Clovis High School. Did I say, Solar? Yes, owned Solar.  Wonderful spacious floor plan featuring 3 bedroom + additional isolated 4th bedroom (1/2 garage conversion). As you enter the home, you are greeted with a step-down formal living or family room and cozy stone fireplace. All open to kitchen and informal or formal eating area. Lots of windows throughout allow for great views of pool and backyard area.  Kitchen is light and bright with Stainless Steel Appliances. Spacious bedrooms and full guest hallway bath with dual sinks. Large and spacious master suite features sitting area, dual closets and patio access to backyard and pool area. Your backyard oasis awaits. Whether sitting on the patio with friends or swimming in your pool, relaxation and entertaining at it's best. Contact agent for additional information.
